    "description": "It's crunch time with these golden, crumbed turkey steaks. Fry until golden and crisp and pair with a warm kimchi potato salad that hums with heat and tang. Packing in the goodness has never tasted better. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
